section.div: Research and development (R&D) is crucial for the enhancement of industrial productivity, especially in the AI era, where the core aspects of R&D are mainly focused on data and models. We are committed to automate these high-value generic R&D processes through our open source R&D automation tool RD-Agent, which let AI drive data-driven AI.
GraphRAG using Local LLMs - Features robust API and multiple apps for Indexing/Prompt Tuning/Query/Chat/Visualizing/Etc. This is meant to be the ultimate GraphRAG/KG local LLM app.
Collection of awesome LLM apps with RAG using OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini and opensource models.
